{"tid":1000710,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屙左舊屎？","createTime":"2019-01-29T15:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T07:35:32.000Z","uid":219809,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"be40dd742fd5146630412521e1ec3b464a49375c","tid":1000710,"uid":219809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:02:48.000Z","msg":"頭先10:40分係屋企感覺到屎意 入左去廁所屙屎<br />\n40分入43分就完事 整個過程好順暢 只有一舊屎屙<br />\n我習慣兩格紙巾抿一次屎忽 因為唔想浪費<br />\n拎起紙巾大力摩擦屎眼 慕求係要清潔得盡善盡美<br />\n為左確保無哂屎積 我就檢查下張紙巾<br />\n點知發覺一點兒屎色都無 甚至近乎全新未用過一樣<br />\n以防萬一 我就聞下有冇味 無色無味 不以任何意識形態存在 <br />\n更神奇既事係 我望向屎兜 竟然連舊屎都唔見埋<br />\n呢刻我只係反覆咁諗緊同一個問題，「我係咪有屙到屎？」<br />\n<br />\n最後贈一首徐志摩既作品《再別康橋》<br />\n悄悄的我走了，<br />\n正如我稍稍的來；<br />\n我擦一擦屎眼，<br />\n不知是否曾屙屎。<br />\n<br />\nPs:真人真事"},{"pid":"d9b49bd3946b7336528688ae495d6c717ba147bf","tid":1000710,"uid":223757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ee849694f24ae0fb76fa84c746f814a3080b190","tid":1000710,"uid":199902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:30:01.000Z","msg":"好一個藝術派啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acb867dbd2e5314bec366e5a8e67d6617d61b6b5","tid":1000710,"uid":69779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:15:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4762532f26143fdfdbc87beab45f56b74124f25","tid":1000710,"uid":226387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"e96a47d77e759d608698345f6df58c33c6d8d86a","tid":1000710,"uid":219809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b49bd3946b7336528688ae495d6c717ba147bf","tid":1000710,"uid":223757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T15:05:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T01:19:10.000Z","msg":"屙屎係有感 只係舊屎唔見左"},{"pid":